DOCKER

It is a tool designed to make it easier to 
build , deploy and run applications by using containers
Problem before docker

Dependency version mismatch from one Env to another
Library corrupted
Software upgrade

Step-1) 

Contains allow a developer to package up an applications with
all of the parts it needs such as library and other dependencies and
ship it out as one package

docker container : is the running instances of the docker image

docker image : it is the skeleton of the docker file. Created by the developer

docker hub: repository to pulling the docker image